data.text: Hannia Guillen is a Cuban-American actress. She is best known for her portrayal of Paloma Lopez-Fitzgerald on the NBC daytime television soap opera Passions from October 16, 2007 to 2008. She also had a supporting role in an episode of the TV series Burn Notice, playing the upwardly-mobile girlfriend of an Israeli gun runner.
